Search must be by name, surname, check_in_date

We will use ecto dynamic queries for this
https://hexdocs.pm/ecto/dynamic-queries.html

- User can submit nothing in that case we set condition to be always TRUE, since it will return all reservations in such case
condition = true
- We use Enum.reduce to select the pattern for search

## Example
def filter_where(params) do
  Enum.reduce(params, dynamic(true), fn
    {"name", value}, dynamic ->
      dynamic([p], ^dynamic and guest)

    {"surname", value}, dynamic ->
      dynamic([p], ^dynamic and p.category == ^value)

    {"check_in_date", value}, dynamic ->
      dynamic([p], ^dynamic and p.published_at > ^value)

    {_, _}, dynamic ->
      # Not a where parameter
      dynamic
  end)
